{"tid":689432,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【衝擊立會罪成】官稱判監是唯一選擇　游蕙禎不上訴即時服刑","createTime":"2018-06-04T05:39:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-04T14:47:59.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"02b08b77821d69f8cd35833fa971247708d13347","tid":689432,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:39:18.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">【衝擊立會罪成】官稱判監是唯一選擇　游蕙禎不上訴即時服刑</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n青年新政梁頌恆及游蕙禎前年因宣誓風波被拒進入立法會會議廳，二人涉嫌與3名助理強行進入會議進行宣誓，5人早前被裁定非法集結罪成，今被判囚4周。對於游蕙禎作出的求情，署理主任裁判官王詩麗稱，當被告的行為涉及暴力時，法庭將不予理會政治理念及動機，判刑亦與理念無關，判監為唯一考慮，而游在求情信表達的是對家人的歉意，而非對其刑事作為有悔意。<br />\n<br />\n5名被告依次為梁頌恆（31歲）、游蕙禎（26歲）、楊禮康（25歲）、鍾雪瑩（26歲）及張子龍（30歲）。<br />\n<br />\n律師其後於庭外表示，游蕙禎、楊禮康、鍾雪瑩決定不就案件上訴，換言之3人會即時服刑。<br />\n<br />\n雖然游蕙禎在裁決時表明不求情，惟今向法庭呈遞3封求情信，她親撰的求情信指自己未盡孝道，父親患癌時由母親獨力照顧，因忙於社運未為母親分擔；又反省自己為令他人聽到自己想法，欠思量向前衝。<br />\n<br />\n署理主任裁判官王詩麗判刑時指出，案件有嚴重之處，案件涉及多人行事，多達5人共同犯案，眾人由議員辦公室出發，分乘兩電梯前往涉事樓層，並於會議室側門會合，明顯有計劃、有預謀，以各自及共同行為令梁游能夠越過保安防線，進入會議室，眾人明顯知道梁游不獲批准進入會議室，明顯事前已做好準備與保安作出衝突。其間眾人多次身體壓向保安，又辱罵保安，事件令多名保安受傷。眾人亦漠視保安勸告，對昏倒的保安漠不關心，未有即時散開。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">王官續指，各被告非少不更事的年齡，已是二十多歲的成年人，判刑須具阻嚇性，以懲罰暴力生事的人</span>，以及反映公眾對於這類罪行的憂慮及爭議。<span style=\"color: red;\">王官又稱，梁游當時為議員身分，視自己為民意象徵，卻在立法機關犯下刑事罪行，損害立法會的尊嚴，判監是唯一選擇</span>。<br />\n<br />\n梁游聞判後神情平靜，在場支持者散庭後向已進入犯人欄的眾被告表示：「加油」、「頂住啊」。<br />\n<br />\n本身已經定左點判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d3b4c69a16c60f31ea3e860ff1453859e4672a2","tid":689432,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:41:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180604/s00001/1528089725677\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180604%2Fs00001%2F1528089725677&d=kdpm3TGC%2FPzajP3Vx6HhkDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=653cbc7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180604%2Fs00001%2F1528089725677&h=d7627a3f\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180604/s00001/1528089725677</a>"},{"pid":"b956e88648f28c07f0be3beb9f4e6dd9d123d83f","tid":689432,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"事撚旦啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都無法治架啦而家"},{"pid":"588a648dffc7133c2e44c97b9d9b025a8d14600b","tid":689432,"uid":117786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:19:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da90bc4c4993d51d2c311eea4fa4383b09ce423","tid":689432,"uid":26156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:19:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"19e49a9d2fc3b69960148657873170f3bc3840d2","tid":689432,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T06:28:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔洗審直接判算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1102cb27616d2465d89e438a4c9799da0be81ee","tid":689432,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:10:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9d71e1e498d62fce6f81684db368dd7d1448972","tid":689432,"uid":15711,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T07:23:37.000Z","msg":"求仁得仁啦"},{"pid":"4db486e11fab171d64de22c265bcd41ad5ff9c22","tid":689432,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T09:50:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b55d9e76f1b3749940481755a7976c2666de3d","tid":689432,"uid":60665,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b956e88648f28c07f0be3beb9f4e6dd9d123d83f","tid":689432,"uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:42:48.000Z","msg":"事撚旦啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都無法治架啦而家"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:34:46.000Z","msg":"低級法院已經淪陷晒<br />\n藍絲官當道"},{"pid":"0224d580ea8a2e63f9eaf346db11fabade5dc334","tid":689432,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"慘啦<br />\n要俾人通櫃挖閪睇下有冇毒品.."},{"pid":"a0510d41a2e9ca62af2976fb1c97ce5489e788b9","tid":689432,"uid":152589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"072b60840e15e6d5041090cc33c5693b4cfa057d","tid":689432,"uid":11890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:48:44.000Z","msg":"[quote]<span style=\"color: red;\">王官又稱，梁游當時為議員身分，視自己為民意象徵，卻在立法機關犯下刑事罪行，損害立法會的尊嚴，判監是唯一選擇</span>。<br />\n[quote]<br />\n喂 班狗平時唔係成日講梁游宣誓嗰日已經失咗議員身分<br />\n咁衝議會嗰日又點樣當時為議員身分呀<br />\n唔係議員又點樣損害立法會尊嚴呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8ee1c9e023ec99a7cbd7ce9fb5e9951f16790d1","tid":689432,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0224d580ea8a2e63f9eaf346db11fabade5dc334","tid":689432,"uid":3302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:36:33.000Z","msg":"慘啦<br />\n要俾人通櫃挖閪睇下有冇毒品.."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T10:55:26.000Z","msg":"近年轉咗用X光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12e609